4... Nf6
{ After this just develop normally, you can choose to trade dark squared bishops or not, Black has a lot of flexibility here. Remember that you probably want to keep the option of c5 open for later in the opening. Notice that Black already has a lead in development on the kingside and the plans from previous lines should come to mind. }
